      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the hotlines, they don't really change anything. it's just noise. it feels like no matter what i do, the pile just gets bigger. i'm just stuck in this loop of failing and feeling like a burden to everyone around me. it's like there's no actual way out of this cycle except to just... stop.",
